老味, 呢啲咪低質素Post囉，<br />\n成撚日問人指教指教，乜柒都唔Provide俾大家討論<br />\n有咩好指教啫? 屌你十足十 香土咁撚樣, 開撚埋,無討論價值嘅話題<br />\n自己立場又唔講下,打撚完個題目就拍拍屁股走人,<br />\n你不如唔撚好打[請指教]. 就噉話[如題] 咪算柒數囉<br />\n係都貼下圖呀, 屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n淨係請人指教, 成個戇鳩仔<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母浮雲（真毒）<br />\n你條撚皮係唔撚係條條問題都話答唔到你㗎柒頭<br />\n<br />\n答到又繼續推舊post又打5P字<br />\n答唔到又當人冇到所以唔鬼Contribute<br />\n<br />\n成日咁撚得閒上嚟連登出埋啲低質素Post鳩噏問人指教<br />\n不如用啲時間去進修下 醫下你個死人腦好過啦<br />\n<br />\n最後補多次<br />\n浮雲（真毒）我屌你老母"},{"pid":"f33dce3363198a2ebfa38a1b8fd851d304fdddfe","tid":2255581,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"642af3fb554b14c9890b47de15544dfa9a0d74a0","tid":2255581,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"走廊用錫紙做牆紙包實直通入房<br />\n之後速度會快過6G <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"上網速度快過烤檸檬雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.reynoldskitchens.com/sites/default/files/styles/hero_image/public/recipes/foil_wrapped_roasted_turkey_0.jpeg?itok=H0G5yDoT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reynoldskitchens.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fhero_image%2Fpublic%2Frecipes%2Ffoil_wrapped_roasted_turkey_0.jpeg%3Fitok%3DH0G5yDoT&h=7d4c953a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"144ff1b441ac57724d3c77156e03d4641ff244fc","tid":2255581,"uid":28590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"可以<br />\n我公司寫字樓d wifi 都係靠中央冷氣傳送，<br />\n比起就咁行router 更快更可靠"},{"pid":"1d4f5d3a2ee534de9c7512923237c9cfd59556cc","tid":2255581,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"放多幾塊鏡折射入去"},{"pid":"b1d20985623bb45a1bf63bde45ccf0099aa829a8","tid":2255581,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"關於風扇問題，樓豬應該去硬件台喎"},{"pid":"e1fc39bc1c79d892a9c5f4fe6d2610c8e7a69a97","tid":2255581,"uid":